<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11035</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>15885</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“巴布斯从监狱逃走了。”罗西想，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>15885</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>17902</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我得帮忙去抓他！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>17902</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>21903</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西朝着朋友们大声喊道：</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>21903</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>25904</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗨，朋友们！等会儿学校见。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>25904</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29154</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我忘了带作业！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29154</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>33654</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>特勒尔看着罗西匆匆离开。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>33654</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>38155</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯……”他说，“真想知道……”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>38155</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41158</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他又摇了摇头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41158</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44401</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不对，她应该不是。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44401</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>48153</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快，罗西就飞上了天空。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>48153</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>53152</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她落在美罗城监狱的停车场里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>53152</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>57657</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一辆监狱囚车翻倒在地上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>57657</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>61570</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> 监狱的栅栏上有一个大洞。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>61570</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>66401</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>史密斯侦探正在跟两个狱警谈话。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>66401</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>68953</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他拿着笔和笔记本。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>68953</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>73453</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>狱警看上去很紧张。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>73453</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>78806</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西咧着嘴笑了。“天啊！侦探先生。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>78806</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>82155</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我不知道你被关进监狱了呢！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>82155</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>87153</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>史密斯侦探转向火箭女孩儿的方向。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>87153</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>91113</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在不是开玩笑的时候，火箭女孩儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>91113</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>94485</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有一个非常危险的犯人逃走了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>94485</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>97985</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我已经知道了。”罗西说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>97985</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>102237</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>史密斯侦探重新转向两个狱警。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>102237</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>104984</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“跟我说说那个犯人吧。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>104984</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>107985</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他叫巴布斯，对吧？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>107985</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>110485</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个狱警点点头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>110485</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>115736</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他是美罗城最坏的犯人之一。他是个小丑。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>115736</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>119988</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>史密斯侦探的笔掉到了地上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>119988</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>123736</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你说他是个小......小丑？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>123736</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>126737</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对的。”那个狱警说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>126737</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>130986</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>史密斯侦探的脸变得苍白。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>130986</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>134238</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西捅了捅侦探的肩膀。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>134238</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>137238</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“侦探先生，您还好吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>137238</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>140487</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>史密斯侦探什么都没说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>140487</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142989</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西看着狱警。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142989</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>146487</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“ 那么巴布斯是怎么逃走的？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>146487</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>148989</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>女狱警发着抖。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>148989</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>152236</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我带着巴布斯从监狱里出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>152236</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>155735</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们打算把他送到别的监狱。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>155735</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>160987</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当我走出来的时候，他的同伙在黑暗中等着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>160987</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>166489</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们抢了巴布斯，逃走了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>166489</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>169985</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他的同伙有谁？”罗西问，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>169985</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>172270</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们看清楚他们了吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>172270</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>175285</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第一个狱警点点头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>175285</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>180790</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“当然。他们也是小丑，跟巴布斯一样。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>180790</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185285</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>史密斯侦探看上去很不舒服。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185285</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>189787</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“侦探先生，您今天怎么了？”罗西问，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>189787</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192785</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你的行为有点古怪。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192785</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>197289</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就在这时，史密斯侦探的手机响了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>197289</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>202539</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>手机在他的口袋里，他好像没听到。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>202539</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>205939</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“史密斯侦探！”罗西说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>205939</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>209669</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你的手机在响。你不接吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>209669</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>214919</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯？”史密斯侦探突然看着罗西。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>214919</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>217172</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦！是我的手机。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>217172</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>222172</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>史密斯侦探从口袋里掏出手机。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>222172</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>228171</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“喂？什么？哦……嗯，好吧。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>228171</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>232667</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我想我们会……嗯……去查看一下的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>232667</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>237168</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>史密斯侦探挂了电话，看着罗西。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>237168</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>242419</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“刚才一名警察发现一辆小丑车在西街上超速行驶。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>242419</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>246420</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那肯定是巴布斯！”罗西说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>246420</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>249170</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们得赶到那儿，侦探先生。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>249170</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>256172</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们……侦探先生？您在哪儿？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>